==Definition==

<b>deuce</b> (<i>noun</i>)
# (<i>[[playing_cards]]</i>) The [[two]] card.
# (<i>sports</i>) In [[tennis]], when both players have the same number of points and one can win by scoring two additional points.
:Ex. <i>40-40</i>
# (some kind of epithet?)
:Ex. <i>my, what a clever <b>deuce</b> he is!</i>

